dct_title_s: Phelps and Engisn's Travellers' Guide and Map of the United States
dct_alternative_sm: Phelp's and Ensign's travellers' guide and map of the United States : containing the roads, distances, steam boat & canal routes & c.
dct_description_sm: Engraved by: J. Wells, Brooklyn, L.I.
Map includes 15 very small insets with maps of vicinities of principal cities.
Includes diagrammatic views of principal rivers and mountains of the world.
Below map are scenes of events of American history, portraits of presidents and King Philip.
"Engraved on steel by J. Wells, Brooklyn, L. I."
